text.data-name: Machine highlights ambiguous terms in a claim and generate questions to assist fact-checking investigation

text.data-name:
1. Highlight ambiguous terms in a claim
2. Generate questions from these ambiguous terms for fact-checkers to conduct further investigation
Questions for further investigation: Who in the Muslim Brotherhood state this sentence? How likely people in the Muslim Brotherhood will end the peace? What kinds of caliphate?

tspan.tspan: Who in the Muslim Brotherhood state this sentence?

text.data-name: People in the Muslim Brotherhood openly stated they want to declare war on Israel and they would end the peace agreement with Israel and they would work towards instituting a caliphate.
